I am in a cross-teaming guild and I really don't see immy healing as a real issue any more.  When we come across a rival guild there is enough team distribution that you really don't have to worry about it because once the fight swings one way or the other it's fairly decisive.  When we encounter a rival guild that is pure-team, our like team sits down and waits for the outcome.
<br />

<br />
Small scale PVP is a different story where immy-healing is much more frequent.  My solution has been to leave and realize there is no honor in the fight or bring back someone that can PVP the immy.
